install : npm install prettier -D
  
Add this to json : "scripts": {"format": "prettier --write .","format-check": "prettier --check ."}

To Forrmet All the files : npm run format

To Check Forrmet All the files : npm run format-check
  
Example prettier config   (.......)
.prettierrc
{
  "semi": true,
  "singleQuote": true,
  "trailingComma": "all",
  "printWidth": 100,
  "tabWidth": 2,
  "useTabs": false,
  "bracketSpacing": true,
  "jsxSingleQuote": false,
  "arrowParens": "always",
  "endOfLine": "lf",
  "htmlWhitespaceSensitivity": "css"
}
Example prettier Ignore config   (.......)
.prettierignore
node_modules
build
dist
public
*.min.js
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
SolidjsApp
